OL,3,CAlmost 300 students to have university
OL,4,Coffers pulled after courses scrapped
OL,6,FAlmost 300 students who were set to
OL,7,Fstart studying in Leicester this
OL,8,FSeptember will have their offers
OL,9,Fcancelled, a union has claimed, after
OL,10,Fthe University of Leicester closed
OL,11,Ftheir courses.
OL,13,FAfter months of consultation, which
OL,14,Fsparked protests and industrial action
OL,15,Flate last year, earlier this month the
OL,16,Funiversity confirmed that its Modern
OL,17,FLanguages and Film Studies courses
OL,18,Fwould be shut down.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774289155
OL,3,CAlmost 300 students to have university
OL,4,Coffers pulled after courses scrapped
OL,6,FThe University and Colleges Union
OL,7,F(UCU) said the fact the decision was
OL,8,Fmade part-way through the UCAS
OL,9,Fadmissions cycle meant hundreds of
OL,10,Fhopeful students would now face their
OL,11,Foffers being rescinded - and also mean
OL,12,Fthe loss of 17 jobs.
OL,14,FThe union's branch co-chair, Dr Joseph
OL,15,FChoonara, said he was "absolutely
OL,16,Fappalled" by the decision."This will
OL,17,Fdiminish the chances students have to
OL,18,Fstudy these subjects in the East
OL,19,FMidlands," he said.
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@IO]{D@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
