OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774289155
OL,3,CAlmost 300 students to have university
OL,4,Coffers pulled after courses scrapped
OL,6,F"And it's also a real blow to the
OL,7,Fstaff members who have been fighting
OL,8,Fto prevent the closures in recent
OL,9,Fmonths."
OL,11,FThe university has announced that,
OL,12,Ffollowing reviews, no compulsory
OL,13,Fredundancies will be made in the
OL,14,Fhistory or School of Education
OL,15,Fdepartments.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
