PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774289155
OL,3,CAlmost 300 students to have university
OL,4,Coffers pulled after courses scrapped
OL,6,FHowever, consultations over the
OL,7,FChemistry and Geography, Geology and
OL,8,Fthe Environment courses are still
OL,9,Fongoing. They are due to close at the
OL,10,Fend of the month, with decisions over
OL,11,Ftheir futures set to come in the
OL,12,Fmiddle of May.
OL,14,FThe UCU Leicester branch now plans to
OL,15,Fstage more industrial action in the
OL,16,Fcoming days.
OL,18,FITV News Central has approached the
OL,19,FUniversity of Leicester for comment.
